%% TrustyAI Explainability - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Reconciler as PayloadReconciler
    participant Storage as DataSource<br/>(PVC/DB/MinIO)
    participant ModelServer as KServe/ModelMesh<br/>Model Server
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>ServiceMonitor

    Note over Client,Prometheus: Flow 1: ModelMesh Inference Payload Ingestion
    ModelServer->>TrustyAI: POST /consumer/kserve/v2<br/>HTTP 80/TCP plaintext
    TrustyAI->>Reconciler: ConsumerEndpoint processes payload
    Reconciler->>Storage: Store reconciled inference record

    Note over Client,Prometheus: Flow 2: KServe CloudEvent Inference Payload Ingestion
    ModelServer->>TrustyAI: CloudEvent (org.kubeflow.serving.inference.*)<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP plaintext
    TrustyAI->>Reconciler: CloudEventConsumer processes event
    Reconciler->>Storage: Store reconciled inference record

    Note over Client,Prometheus: Flow 3: Scheduled Metric Computation & Prometheus Scraping
    TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: PrometheusScheduler (cron trigger)
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Read historical inference data
    Storage-->>TrustyAI: Inference records
    TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: Compute SPD, DIR, drift metrics
    TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: Publish to PrometheusPublisher
    Prometheus->>TrustyAI: GET /q/metrics<br/>HTTP 80/TCP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    TrustyAI-->>Prometheus: trustyai_spd, trustyai_dir, drift metrics

    Note over Client,Prometheus: Flow 4: Explainability Request (LIME/SHAP/CF)
    Client->>Route: POST /explainers/local/lime<br/>HTTP plaintext
    Route->>TrustyAI: Forward request
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Read historical data for context
    Storage-->>TrustyAI: Historical inference records
    TrustyAI->>ModelServer: Inference request<br/>gRPC or HTTP plaintext
    ModelServer-->>TrustyAI: Inference response
    TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: Compute LIME explanation
    TrustyAI-->>Route: JSON explanation response
    Route-->>Client: LIME explanation result

    Note over Client,Prometheus: Flow 5: Fairness Metric Request
    Client->>Route: POST /metrics/group/fairness/spd<br/>HTTP plaintext
    Route->>TrustyAI: Forward request
    TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: Schedule SPD metric computation
    TrustyAI-->>Route: 200 OK - Metric scheduled
    Route-->>Client: Metric request accepted
